data.description: New listing in desirable Arbor Springs neighborhood across the street from the playground and pool. This  4 bedroom, 2 and 1/2 bath home has even more room to expand with full 1600+ sqft unfinished basement you can make your own. This home has many features including 2 story entry with 10 ft ceilings on the first floor and 9 ft upstairs and in the basement.  There is a formal dining room, home office with custom built-in shelves, open concept kitchen, breakfast nook and great room.  The primary bedroom has an en-suite bathroom with a double vanity, separate tub and shower, linen closet and 10x11 walk in closet.  The second bathroom is a jack-n-jill that also opens to the hallway.  Upstairs you'll find a bonus room almost as big as the great room.  Outside features a large deck with built in hot tub and fully fenced back yard.  The 3 car garage is oversized to fit all your needs.
